c2cq2OE9SiaLKahL3Mk0KA.description: A collection of low-level building blocks.

U5iIpgd8SHCk7pvaciVLTQ.name: Holarchy Base Memory Mailbox Flag
U5iIpgd8SHCk7pvaciVLTQ.description: A primitive cell process that signals (via process step transition) when some actor has put a message in the mailbox namespace.

z_mTe02hSWmaM1iRO1pBeA.name: Abstract Frame Latch
z_mTe02hSWmaM1iRO1pBeA.description: Frame latch provides a way to create a value and attach a model that transitions between waiting and updated process steps whenever the value is written. This allows consumers of the value (other OPM typically) to monitor frame latch process to know when the value is updated so that they can read the new value and do whatever they need to with it.

iyvk_9vhRn2qvrjOes5v7Q.name: Frame Latch: Write
iyvk_9vhRn2qvrjOes5v7Q.description: Writes the value made observable by frame latch APM instance.

MDVBKW89TvO9T62Ge7GmNg.description: Holarchy Core CellLibrary packages standard logic and shared memory cell process step transition operators and action plug-ins that are loaded automatically into every CellProcessor cellular process runtime environment instance.

orTbEFR_Q-u-qqEqP8OUBA.name: Holarchy Core Cell
orTbEFR_Q-u-qqEqP8OUBA.description: Shared low-level TransitionOperator and ControllerAction's for interacting with cell processes running inside of an ObservableProcessController instance.

RW8Y2O-kRNSv87yXT962wQ.description: A collection of TranitionOperator plug-ins that implement generic logic functions AND, OR, NOT, TRUE.
